{
  "id": "663742db7d9b7500240f7ece",
  "title": "明朝体記法",
  "created": 1714897629,
  "updated": 1783515556,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "663742db7d9b7500240f7ece",
      "text": "明朝体記法",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1714897629,
      "updated": 1714897629
    },
    {
      "id": "663742de71b3c20000189444",
      "text": "code:style.css",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1714897630,
      "updated": 1714897704
    },
    {
      "id": "6637431b71b3c20000189445",
      "text": "\t.deco-\\+.deco-\\! {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1714897691,
      "updated": 1783511086
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e382d000000000033f714",
      "text": "\t  /* font-family: serif; */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511086,
      "updated": 1783511116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e383e000000000033f716",
      "text": "\t  font-family: var(--serif, \"\"), serif, var(--icons, AppIcons);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511103,
      "updated": 1783512071
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e488e0000000000de8ad0",
      "text": "\t  font-size-adjust: var(--serif-font-size-adjust, unset);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783515279,
      "updated": 1783515305
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3834000000000033f715",
      "text": "\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511092,
      "updated": 1783511093
    },
    {
      "id": "6637433271b3c20000189446",
      "text": "[+! [明朝体]で表記されます]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1714897714,
      "updated": 1783511804
    },
    {
      "id": "6637434071b3c20000189447",
      "text": "\t[+! フリーの明朝体フォントを入れてないとMS明朝なのであまり綺麗じゃない？]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1714897728,
      "updated": 1714901558
    },
    {
      "id": "6637445c71b3c20000719af6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1714898012,
      "updated": 1714898092
    },
    {
      "id": "66cefdfeed60e60000369f33",
      "text": "游明朝にしたらええんちゃう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1724841471,
      "updated": 1724841485
    },
    {
      "id": "66cf033a71b3c20000e2eb8b",
      "text": "\tブラウザの標準明朝体フォントの設定が使用される[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1724842810,
      "updated": 1724842827
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e386b000000000033f717",
      "text": "\t[BIZ UD明朝]がええんちゃう？[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511148,
      "updated": 1783511184
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e38cf000000000033f71a",
      "text": "\t　デバイス標準の明朝体は正直物凄く気持ち悪い。生理的不快感が強い #ディスレクシア傾向",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511248,
      "updated": 1783511307
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3892000000000033f718",
      "text": "\t　あと Android Chrome などのモバイルブラウザはデフォルトフォントを変更できない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511186,
      "updated": 1783511321
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3923000000000033f71c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511331,
      "updated": 1783511331
    },
    {
      "id": "66cf035871b3c20000e2eb8c",
      "text": "[+! 使えないと思ったら明朝体の設定にゴシック体のフォント名が入ってた][bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1724842841,
      "updated": 1724842887
    },
    {
      "id": "66cf039471b3c20000e2eb8e",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/8db581a3582499f91604eff201f9451b]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1724842901,
      "updated": 1724842902
    },
    {
      "id": "66cf035871b3c20000e2eb8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1724842841,
      "updated": 1724842841
    },
    {
      "id": "663744ab71b3c20000719af7",
      "text": "[Usercss.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1714898091,
      "updated": 1714898463
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3c18000000000033f735",
      "text": "2026-07-08 `font-family:`に[FontAwesomeをScrapbox全体で有効にする]（変数`--icons:`）を追加しました[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783512088,
      "updated": 1783512145
    },
    {
      "id": "6637461d71b3c2000080697e",
      "text": "2026-07-08 変数`--serif:`及び変数`--serif-font-size-adjust`を導入しました[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1714898461,
      "updated": 1783515353
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e399b000000000033f720",
      "text": " UserCSSのサンプル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511452,
      "updated": 1783511493
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e39c5000000000033f725",
      "text": " [project名を明朝体にする]を参照のこと",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511493,
      "updated": 1783511508
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e392b000000000033f71d",
      "text": " code:example.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511340,
      "updated": 1783511407
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3a76000000000033f728",
      "text": "  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zilla+Slab:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap');",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511670,
      "updated": 1783511670
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3ab0000000000033f72a",
      "text": "  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=BIZ+UDMincho&display=swap');",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511728,
      "updated": 1783511730
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e39b0000000000033f722",
      "text": "  body {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511473,
      "updated": 1783511679
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e39b0000000000033f723",
      "text": "    --serif: \"Zilla Slab\", \"Roboto Serif\", \"Roboto Slab\", \"Comic Sans MS\", \"BIZ UD明朝\", \"BIZ UDMincho\", \"BIZ UDP明朝\", \"BIZ UDPMincho\", \"Yu Mincho Medium\", sans-serif;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511473,
      "updated": 1783515556
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e48790000000000de8acf",
      "text": "    --serif-font-size-adjust: 0.51;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783515258,
      "updated": 1783515273
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e39b0000000000033f724",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511473,
      "updated": 1783515254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e3964000000000033f71e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783511396,
      "updated": 1783511396
    }
  ]
}